page.title: 16HOME LIFE 2
page.content: cats. I watch television usually "Let's Pretend' then set off for school. I get to school about l2.55. I have registration then go to my next lesson. End of school bell at 3.35. I get home about 4.oo. I watch television for a little while then do any homework that has to be done for the next day. I always do my homework late. After my homework is done I go up to my bedroom and have a muck about. At 5.3O I have my tea, usually while watching television. After tea I get ready to go to Guides. Me and my cousin help at Brownies, we are Pack Leaders. After Brownies it is Guides. We always have a muck about at Guides, it's a laugh.At 9.OO my mum comes to pick me up. When I get home I usually have my supper, watch a bit of T.V., then I go to my room, get undressed,wash,get into bed and read.
